author: Drew Griffin, Curt Devine, Scott Bronstein and Nelli Black, CNN
title: Documents show the struggle to keep pace with the pandemic at just one US lab company
description: As the US health care system has scrambled to track the spread of coronavirus, one of the nation's largest commercial labs has faced a backlog of tests that ballooned in the last two weeks, and has delayed results in some cases up to 10 days.
